		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">i am still trying to get my ppu to work correctly and my emulator fails your test, infact only shows a black screen.</div>
<br />
<br />I can't help until you start describing your situation more precisely. As I remember, we last left off in e-mail with me asking whether your emulator supported CHR RAM games, like Metroid and Kid Icarus. My test ROMs load the CHR data dynamically, so if you don't support CHR RAM, they'll obviously put up a blank screen. I should change them to use CHR ROM in the future.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


