	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nestress uses a wavy scanline-by-scanline scroller at the beginning just to show off.  If you don't draw each scanline separately based on the scroll registers at that time, it will just scroll the whole screen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


